  "text": "The matching process is to some extent similar to [CITATION_1] , but instead of searching the whole image, we propose to employ the particle filter algorithm to search the best position for the template. This has the potential to considerably reduce computational requirements. Compared to the particle filter used for person tracking, the weight of each particle is changed to:",
